    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small pockets made in the waistband of breeches, cummerbund, and other clothing, usually men's clothing or clothing made to imitate menswear, used for carrying a watch, money, or other valuables.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
